  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware, org.springframework.core.Ordered, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware, org.springframework.web.servlet.ViewResolver

    public class FreeMarkerViewResolver
extends org.springframework.web.servlet.view.AbstractTemplateViewResolver
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean
    FreeMarker template view resolver implementation, extending AbstractTemplateViewResolver that extends UrlBasedViewResolver.

    The FreeMarker Configuration property must be set at least. Otherwise this throws IllegalStateException during initialization. In the bean initialization phase, this retrieves ObjectWrapperAndUnwrapper from the Configuration and instantiate the internal page object (PageContextServlet) for JSP tag library usages, ServletContextHashModel property for servlet context attribute accesses and TaglibFactory property for JSP tag library usages.
